DeSantis fires back at Disney's distortions. Pelosi blames "Putin Tax" for high gas prices. Steve Yates, former deputy national security adviser to Vice President Dick Cheney, discusses the war in Ukraine with Clay and Buck. WSJ midterm poll: GOP with 5-point lead, gain with minorities.
